BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20250311T140000Z
DTEND:20250311T150000Z
SUMMARY:BioExcel webinar: Restoring protein glycosylation with GlycoShape
UID:7790fe84-056c-4f2d-8893-8f5d7e95becb
DESCRIPTION:Rebuilding glycosylation is significant for understanding 
 biomolecular structure and function in life sciences. This webinar shows 
 how glycoproteins (for example\, from the Protein Data Bank or from 
 machine learning systems such as AlphaFold and RoseTTAFold) can be 
 restored to their native\, functional state by adding the missing glycan 
 3D information in seconds using GlycoShape.\, 
 https://www.pdc.kth.se/about/events/bioexcel-webinar-restoring-protein-
 glycosylation-with-glycoshape-1.1386203
LOCATION:online
DTSTAMP:20250304T064630Z
END:VEVENT
